---
import LegalLayout from "@/layouts/legal.astro";
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Security"
  description="Learn about how we protect your data and maintain the security of our platform."
>
  <h2>Our Security Commitment</h2>
  <p>
    At ColdJot, security is a top priority. We implement industry-standard
    security measures to protect your data and ensure the safety of our
    platform.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Protection</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>All data is encrypted in transit using TLS 1.3</li>
    <li>Sensitive data is encrypted at rest using AES-256</li>
    <li>Regular security audits and penetration testing</li>
    <li>Secure data centers with 24/7 monitoring</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Account Security</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Two-factor authentication support</li>
    <li>Strong password requirements</li>
    <li>Session management and automatic timeouts</li>
    <li>Login attempt monitoring and rate limiting</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Infrastructure Security</h2>
  <p>Our infrastructure is hosted on secure cloud providers with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Regular security patches and updates</li>
    <li>Network isolation and firewalls</li>
    <li>DDoS protection</li>
    <li>Continuous monitoring and alerting</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Compliance</h2>
  <p>
    We maintain compliance with relevant security standards and regulations:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>GDPR compliance for EU data protection</li>
    <li>Regular security assessments</li>
    <li>Employee security training</li>
    <li>Incident response procedures</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Reporting Security Issues</h2>
  <p>
    If you discover a security vulnerability, please report it to our security
    team at <a href="mailto:security@coldjot.com">security@coldjot.com</a>. We
    take all security reports seriously and will respond promptly.
  </p>

  <h2>Updates and Notifications</h2>
  <p>
    We continuously monitor and update our security measures. Users will be
    notified of any significant security updates or incidents that may affect
    their data.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>

